00:27:39.975 --> 00:27:41.350
because those
people aren't there

00:27:41.350 --> 00:27:44.930
to work that particular day.

00:27:44.930 --> 00:27:47.620
So typically, if you did this--

00:27:47.620 --> 00:27:50.140
you hire up at the beginning
of each timetable model

00:27:50.140 --> 00:27:51.040
