00:32:11.110 --> 00:32:14.890
So you'll be having high
direct payment costs because

00:32:14.890 --> 00:32:16.390
of the reliance on overtime.

00:32:16.390 --> 00:32:20.440
And that gives you an
overall high cost solution

00:32:20.440 --> 00:32:22.840
beyond some point where
you get a good balance

00:32:22.840 --> 00:32:26.860
between the costs of overtime
and the cost of fixed fringe

00:32:26.860 --> 00:32:27.970
benefits.

00:32:27.970 --> 00:32:31.960
Then you'll get a sweet spot
you'll want to try and operate.

00:32:31.960 --> 00:32:34.655
And you want to avoid
